Subject: rPSA-2008-0128-1 firefox

rPath Security Advisory: 2008-0128-1
Published: 2008-03-27
Products:
    rPath Linux 1

Rating: Major
Exposure Level Classification:
    Indirect User Deterministic Unauthorized Access
Updated Versions:
    firefox=conary.rpath.com@rpl:1/2.0.0.13-0.1-1

rPath Issue Tracking System:
    https://issues.rpath.com/browse/RPL-2401

References:
    http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2008-1233
    http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2008-1234
